<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.264614>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Adults in DV (left), VV (right). A: HT ♀ of Heteropsis tornado Lees, Allaoui & Aduse-Poku, sp. nov. (NHMUK 010289143; Anjanaharibe Sud). B: PT ♀ of Ht. tornado (Marojejy; KAP-MAD 1403). C: ♂ of Ht. tornado (‘ Mahassabe’) [from colour transparency]. D: ♀ of Ht. tornado (‘ Mahassabe’; BMNH (E) # 674881). Scale bar: 30 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/264614/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.264598>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Venation and wing patterning diagram of a fairly typical species of Heteropsis from Madagascar (Heteropis antahala group; ♂), DV. Sdbp = Supra-discocellular brush and patch. Cub = Cubital brush. Ventral banding: Cb = Costal bars. Mf = Median fleck (pale highlight). Mb = Median band. PMb = Premedian band. Ore = Ocellus ring extension. Pml = Premarginal line. Sml = Submarginal line." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/264598/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.264627>
    dc:description "FIGURE 30. Distribution maps. A. Purple: Heteropsis vanewrighti Lees, sp. nov. Green: Ht. pauliani Lees, sp. nov. Yellow: Ht. mimetica Lees & Kremen, sp. nov. Light blue: Ht. hazovola Lees & Raharitsimba, sp. nov. Turquoise: Ht. imerina Lees, sp. nov. [northern populations overlapping with Ht. vanewrighti and Ht. pauliani are not shown]. Pink: Ht. westwoodi Lees, sp. nov. B. Red: Ht. avaratra Lees & Kremen, sp. nov. Light blue: Ht. kremenae Lees, sp. nov. Fawn: Ht. vertigo Lees & Raharitsimba, sp. nov. C. Ochre: Ht. roussettae Lees & Kremen, sp. nov. Slate-blue: Ht. menamenoides Lees, sp. nov. Olive: Ht. lanyvary Lees, sp. nov. Dark green: Ht. borgo Lees, sp. nov. Light green: Ht. barbarae Lees & Kremen, sp. nov. Brown: Ht. oberthueri Lees, sp. nov. Dark pink: Ht. tianae Lees & Kremen, sp. nov. D. Mid green: Ht. sogai Lees, sp. nov. Dark brown: Ht. tornado Lees, Allaoui & Aduse-Poku, sp. nov. Lilac: Ht. harveyi Lees & Kremen, sp. nov. Light brown: centraleastern populations of Ht. harveyi complex. Scale bar: 500 km." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/264627/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.264616>
    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Adults in DV (left), VV (right). A: HT ♂ of Heteropsis lanyvary Lees, sp. nov. (Tsaratanana; NHMUK 010289144). B: PT ♀ of Ht. lanyvary (Tsaratanana; NHMUK 010289145). C: HT ♂ of Mycalesis ankova Ward, 1870 (‘ Madagascar’; BMNH (E) 673767). D: LT ♂ of Culapa pallida Oberthür, 1916 (‘ Antsianaka’, BMNH (E) 673775). E: LT ♂ of Culapa ornata Oberthür, 1916 (‘ Madagascar’; BMNH (E) 673678; Ht. turbata (Butler, 1880 )). Scale bar: 30 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/264616/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.264615>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. ♂ genitalia in LV (left), DV (right). A: Heteropsis tornado Lees, Allaoui & Aduse-Poku, sp. nov., ♂ genitalia (‘ Mahassabe’; 362 DL) (detail of valve inset; drawing modified after Lees, 1997: 106); not to scale. B: ♂ genitalia of Ht. lanyvary. (left: DL- 05 - 761; right: DL- 05 - 845). C: ♂ genitalia of Heteropsis barbarae sp. nov. (Antsamanarana R., Masoala; CK 30, 141 DL). D: ♂ genitalia of Heteropsis menamenoides Lees, sp. nov. (Mt. Bekolosy; DLBEK 94 _ 180; 231 DL). Scale bar: 3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/264615/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.264604>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Adults in DV (left), VV (right) or in natural postures. A: HT ♂ of Heteropsis harveyi Lees & Kremen, sp. nov. (NHMUK 010289119). B: PT ♀ of Ht. harveyi (NHMUK 010289121). C: HT ♂ of Henotesia andravahana ab. marmorata Aurivillius, 1911 (NHRS-TOBI 000000050). D: pair of Ht. harveyi in copula (Maromizaha, photo courtesy Lance Featherstone). E: ♂ of Ht. imerina (Ankazomivady, 23 / 03 / 2003, photo: D. C. Lees), for comparison, showing relatively produced ‘ tail’ on HW vein M 3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/264604/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

